    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-4">
            <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                <button class="w-full flex justify-between items-center p-4 focus:outline-none faq-toggle">
                    <span class="font-medium">What is your return policy?</span>
                    <i data-feather="chevron-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="p-4 border-t border-gray-200 hidden">
                    <p class="text-gray-700">We offer a 30-day return policy for unused items in original packaging. Machines have a 90-day warranty period for returns.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
